propel.core.collections.queues

Class SharedQueue<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • propel.core.collections.queues.SharedQueue<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<T>, ISharedQueue<T>, ReifiedIterable<T>, IShared

    public class SharedQueue<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements ISharedQueue<T>
    A type-aware thread-safe queue implementation. This collection allows null items to be inserted. Instantiate using e.g.: new SharedQueue<String>(){}; -OR- new SharedQueue<String>(String.class);
